{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"assign"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"targetCoordinate"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"By default, this property is set to an invalid coordinate, indicating that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"there is no target. In course tracking mode, the target forms one of two foci","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"in the viewport, the other being the user location annotation. Typically, this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"property is set to a destination or waypoint in a real-time navigation scene.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"As the user annotation moves toward the target, the map automatically zooms in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to fit both foci optimally within the viewport.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This property has no effect if the ","type":"text"},{"code":"userTrackingMode","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" property is set to a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"value other than ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserTrackingMode\/MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Changing the value of this property updates the map view with an animated","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"transition. If you don’t want to animate the change, use the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"-setTargetCoordinate:animated:","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" method instead.","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/targetcoordinate"]}],"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/targetCoordinate","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(py)targetCoordinate","symbolKind":"property","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"targetCoordinate"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"targetCoordinate","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L752","fileName":"MLNMapView.h"},"title":"targetCoordinate"},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The geographic coordinate that is the subject of observation as the user"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"location is being tracked."}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","role":"collection","title":"MapLibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/targetCoordinate":{"abstract":[{"text":"The geographic coordinate that is the subject of observation as the user","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"l